-- Google, Twitter Seek to Help Defend News Service in Bank Research Lawsuit
-- Michael Hytha
-- 2010-06-22T00:55:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/google-twitter-seek-to-help-defend-news-service-in-bank-research-lawsuit.html

          
          
             Google Inc. and Twitter Inc. sought
to help defend Theflyonthewalll.com, an online financial news
service, from a lawsuit by banks including Barclays Plc accusing
it of “free riding” on their research reports about companies.  
          
          


  


        